  body
    nav
      ul
        li: a(href="#home") Home
        li: a(href="#about") Try It!
        li: a(href="#try-it") About

    h1 ð–¦¹ B.A.I. BOT ð–¦¹

    main
      h2 Hi art student! This is a tool that analyzes the color theory in your artwork, and uses AI to give you advice. Try it out!
      
      h3 Describe your artwork. Things you can include:
      ul
        li What emotions the artwork should evoke
        li What medium you used to make the work
        li Questions you would like to be answered
      input(type="text" id="questionInput" placeholder="Enter your description")
      
      h3 Upload an image of your artwork.
      #dropBox
        p Drag and drop an image here or click to select a file.
      input(type="file" id="imageInput" style="display: none;")
      
      button#analyzeButton Analyze Image
      
      footer
        p#answer

    script(src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/axios/dist/axios.min.js")
    script(type="module" src="script.js")
